  "title": "Warehouse Manager",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking an experienced Warehouse Manager to lead our warehouse operations, manage inventory, and drive process improvements. Min 2 years of experience in a similar role required.</p><p></p><p>Responsibilities:</p><p>- Oversee daily warehouse operations, including receiving, storing, and shipping</p><p>- Manage inventory accuracy and implement stock control measures</p><p>- Lead a team of warehouse staff and ensure productivity targets are met</p><p>- Improve warehouse processes and maintain a safe working environment</p><p>- Coordinate with other departments (e.g., logistics, sales)</p><p></p><p>Requirements:</p><p>- Min 2 years of experience as a Warehouse Manager or similar role</p><p>- Diploma or above in Logistics, Supply Chain, or related field (preferred)</p><p>- Proven track record in managing a warehouse team</p><p>- Able to work independently and drive results</p><p>- Reliable, hardworking, and a team player</p><p></p><p>Benefits:</p><p>- Annual leave</p><p>- Medical benefits</p><p>- Other allowances (transport, etc.)</p>",
